keyMappings:
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap gT
unmap gt
unmap J
unmap K
unmap f
unmap F
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map <a-h> previousTab
map <a-˙> previousTab # for mac
map <a-l> nextTab
map <a-¬> nextTab # for mac
map g' firstTab
map g; lastTab
map <a-π> togglePinTab # for mac
map <a-µ> toggleMuteTab # for mac
map R reload hard
map <a-k> moveTabRight
map <a-j> moveTabLeft
map <a-˚> moveTabRight # for mac
map <a-∆> moveTabLeft # for mac
map <a-K> moveTabRight count=1000
map <a-J> moveTabLeft count=1000
map <a-> moveTabRight count=1000 # for mac
map <a-Ô> moveTabLeft count=1000 # for mac
